==English==
{{was wotd|2020|August|3}}
===Etymology===
[[File:Høns-2005 (cropped).jpg|thumb|Yardfowl ''(sense 1)'' – chickens raised in a yard]]
From {{compound|en|yard|fowl}}. Sense 2 (“political sycophant”) may allude to the tendency of chickens to gather around a person who is feeding them.
